comment: it's creepy how Dandy's mom's eyes follow him, even if she's dead
the entire reason dandy was so crazy was because he had mommy problems.

"avon lady who's name i don't know..."
priceless tbh

Woah dudes, it's been nine months since i've seen this

And now we know where he got his madness from! Edward Mott was the beginning of it all! I know Dandy was psycho, but I can't help but love his character. He was so twisted, but unlike every other character in this season, he didn't justify his actions as right. He purely did them for his own satisfaction, and he had no problem with that. But anyways, the psychos always end up being my favorites. lol.
What bothers me is I keep thinking that his mothers eyes move to watch him
